                FAQItem(question: "Will it fix my baldness?", answer: "If your hair follicles are completely dead and scarred over, no. If your hair is thinning (miniaturization of the follicles), topical GHK-Cu (especially combined with microneedling) has been clinically proven to enlarge the follicles and stimulate new growth."),
