                FAQItem(question: "Can I use it while taking GLP-1s like Semaglutide?", answer: "Yes, this is highly recommended. GLP-1s cause rapid weight loss, which often leads to loose, sagging skin. GHK-Cu upregulates collagen and elastin production, helping the skin tighten as you lose the fat."),
