                FAQItem(question: "Why does my skin feel sensitive or sunburned?", answer: "This is a neurological side effect called allodynia, reported by a small percentage of users on Tirzepatide and Retatrutide. It is harmless and usually goes away after a few weeks as the body adjusts."),
