                FAQItem(question: "Will it make me fail a drug test?", answer: "Yes. WADA explicitly bans AOD-9604 under the category of Peptide Hormones and Mimetics. It was at the center of a massive doping scandal in the Australian Football League (AFL) in 2013."),
                FAQItem(question: "I've been taking it for a week and haven't lost any weight. Is it fake?", answer: "Probably not. AOD-9604 does not cause rapid water weight loss or suppress your appetite like Ozempic. It simply unlocks fat cells. If you aren't in a caloric deficit and doing cardio, that unlocked fat just goes right back into the cell."),
